$BTC.X Don't listen to the FUD. Bitcoin is not an investment. Bitcoin is not a stock. 

Bitcoin is a **verifiably scarce** and **ownable** piece of code that is transferrable without existing financial infrastructure. 

You can pass it through paper. You can pass it through email. A picture hanging on your wall could have your life savings in it. 

Bitcoin transcends the old-world. 

Do not believe the FUD. Own your keys. Own your coins. 

A coin held is a coin no one else can hold. Stop trading paper Bitcoin. Buy actual Bitcoin and get it in your own hands. 

Contribute and learn. Do not spread idiotic lies. 

Bitcoin has **never been hacked.** Only people have been. 

🧠‽ Bullish
